 19, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "A man walks into a bar in Dublin. He's got shoulders like a bricklayer and hands that remember real work. He orders a pint, pays his tab, and minds his business. Three stools down, a gaggle of university students are debating whether the very existence of men like him is a public health crisis. One of them\u2014a twenty-two-year-old with a gender studies degree and the upper body strength of a damp napkin\u2014declares that traditional masculinity is the root of all societal evil. The big man drinks his pint, stares into the glass, and says nothing. He pays for his silence every single day of his life. That silence ends now.I wrote this book because I watched my country die, and I intend to name the killers.Ireland did not fall to the English. Let us be precise about the matter. The English tried\u2014oh, how they tried. Eight hundred years of attempted extermination. Cromwell's butchery. The deliberate starvation of a million souls while food exports continued under armed guard. Penal laws designed to crush the Catholic p", "large_image": "mFhQwVV8MrVH6fNh.png", "title": "Conrad Riker (@conradnriker)"}, "post_flair_text": "BE\u00a0\u00a0LESS\u00a0\u00a0RETARDED", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsUQNRsA", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 436, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8621442, "raw_content": "", "author": "Bongos", "created": 1778931325221, "profile_picture": "ysGr8cf4pMwv", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "L74ge9wr", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "kentuckylantern.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://kentuckylantern.com/briefs/louisville-democrat-drops-out-of-house-race-after-video-shows-him-taking-election-